TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Linear Aggregation Coefficient as the Dual of the Linear Correlation Coefficient
AU  - Ijiri, Yuji
AB  - [In this paper the linear aggregation coefficient is defined as a measure of the degree of perfectness of a linear aggregation function with respect to a given basic function, and its properties are analyzed in relation to its dual, the linear correlation coefficient.]
C1  - Full publication date: Apr., 1968
