TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Bias of Liviatan's Consistent Estimator in a Distributed Lag Model
AU  - Nagar, A. L.
AU  - Gupta, Y. P.
AB  - [In an earlier article published in the International Economic Review (1963) Liviatan proposed a consistent estimator for a distributed lag model. In the present note we analyze the bias of this estimator to order 1/T, T being the number of observations.]
